'''Gaziosmanpaşa Stadium''' ({{lang-tr|Gaziosmanpaşa Stadyumu}}) is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Tokat]], [[Turkey]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Tokatspor]].  The stadium was opened in 1984 and holds 7,500 people.<ref name="ws">[http://www.worldstadiums.com/middle_east/countries/turkey/black_sea.shtml World Stadiums: Gaziosmanpaşa Stadium] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080118234146/http://www.worldstadiums.com/middle_east/countries/turkey/black_sea.shtml |date=2008-01-18 }}</ref>

