{{Infobox Organization |name = Sindh Rugby Association |image = |size = |motto = |type = [[List of international sport federations|Sports federation]] |formation = |headquarters = [[Pakistan]] |leader_title = |leader_name = |}}
The '''Sindh Rugby Association''' (SRA) is the governing body overseeing [[Rugby union|rugby]] in the [[Sindh]] province of Pakistan. It is a member of the [[Pakistan Rugby Union]].
