The '''Turkish Rugby Federation''' ({{lang|tr|Türkiye Ragbi Federasyonu}}) is the governing body for [[rugby union]]  in [[Turkey]]. It was founded in 2011, and became affiliated to [[Rugby Europe]] in 2012.<ref>[http://www.rugbyeurope.eu/team-77.htm Members] Rugby Europe, 2015.</ref> Turkey is not yet a member of [[World Rugby]].

==Teams==
*[[Turkey national rugby union team|Turkey]] - the national men's rugby union team.
*[[Turkey national rugby union team (sevens)|7s]] - the national men's rugby union seven-a-side team.

